cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.CV, cs.NA, cs.SI

This paper involves the use of machine learning techniques and algorithms to perform classification and regression on various data sets. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with topological data analysis, which suggests that it could belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Additionally, the use of template functions to approximate continuous functions on persistence diagrams could be relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and numerical analysis (cs.NA).
